title: Frituur Veggie Eetboetiek Royal
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Western, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Makes french fries (chips), sandwiches with vegetables, vegetarian meatball, eggplant cakes, vegan spaghetti, soups, organic veggie burgers including sunflowerburger, hazelnutburger, risottoburger. Has vegan mayonaise. Veggie snacks are fried separately from meats.
